metadata.name: Here We Are Now Entertain Us | يلا سلونا
metadata.description:
Metaverse ready

This is an augmented reality piece that can be paired with a physical print. The animation overlays on physical print when viewed through your phone.

The JPEG file is super high res at 8000 x 10000 pixels to create extremely large prints

Holder gets access to a physcial print at cost+shipping. 

Physical prints are limited to 5 prints total. 4 have already been printed at the time of Mint - ie. The first holder gets access to the final edition
